{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01M5ru2C8LMnnNUX8NxJwQ5K","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I need to perform the major code refactoring. The key changes needed for Quarkus:\n\n1. **Remove `persistence.xml`** - Quarkus uses `application.properties` instead\n2. **Remove `beans.xml`** - Quarkus uses its own CDI (Arc) \n3. **Remove `server.xml`** - Liberty-specific\n4. **Remove `microprofile-config.properties`** - moved to `application.properties`\n5. **Change `@PersistenceContext` to `@Inject`** in AbstractDAO\n6. **Change `App.java`** - Remove or simplify the JAX-RS Application class  \n7. **Adapt security filters** for Quarkus (ContainerRequestFilter works in Quarkus too, but with some differences)\n8. **Resource classes** - `@Transactional` should be from `jakarta.transaction`, which Quarkus supports\n9. **SerializerConfig** - needs `@io.quarkus.arc.Unremovable` or alternative approach\n\nLet me now do a massive parallel refactoring:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":532,"cache_read_input_tokens":103873,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":532,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":588},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e4f0ba96-c3d7-44ae-b77e-aba0b53da63a","uuid":"684134da-b580-47f4-8e85-95ccb69f8805"}
