{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_015XkH4GpFRpUiAYYA8nG1Eu","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_012AGQbfMpSF8tyKV9Zw5HuZ","name":"Task","input":{"description":"Refactor all Java source files","subagent_type":"general-purpose","prompt":"I'm migrating a Jakarta EE / Open Liberty application to Quarkus. The project root is: /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output\n\nI need you to make the following changes to multiple files. Read each file first, then edit it.\n\n## KEY CHANGES NEEDED:\n\n### 1. ArticlesResource.java (src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/ArticlesResource.java)\n- Change `@Inject ObjectMapper objectMapper;` to `@Inject @Named(\"wrappingObjectMapper\") ObjectMapper objectMapper;`\n- Add `import jakarta.inject.Named;`\n- Remove `private` from all `@Inject` fields (Quarkus CDI requires package-private or public for injection)\n\n### 2. UsersResource.java (src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/UsersResource.java)\n- Change `@Inject private ObjectMapper objectMapper;` to `@Inject @Named(\"wrappingObjectMapper\") ObjectMapper objectMapper;`\n- Add `import jakarta.inject.Named;`\n- Remove `private` from all `@Inject` fields\n- FIX BUG: The `create` method parameter has `@Context SecurityException context` - this should be `@Context SecurityContext securityContext` (but it's unused, so just keep it or remove it)\n\n### 3. UserResource.java (src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/UserResource.java)\n- Change `@Inject private ObjectMapper objectMapper;` to `@Inject @Named(\"wrappingObjectMapper\") ObjectMapper objectMapper;`\n- Add `import jakarta.inject.Named;`\n- Remove `private` from all `@Inject` fields\n\n### 4. ProfilesResource.java (src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/ProfilesResource.java)\n- Change `@Inject private ObjectMapper objectMapper;` to `@Inject @Named(\"wrappingObjectMapper\") ObjectMapper objectMapper;`\n- Add `import jakarta.inject.Named;`\n- Remove `private` from all `@Inject` fields\n\n### 5. ResourceUtils.java (src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/utils/ResourceUtils.java)\n- Remove `private` from all `@Inject` fields\n\n### 6. BusinessExceptionMapper.java (src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/web/mapper/BusinessExceptionMapper.java)\n- Change `@Inject ObjectMapper objectMapper;` to `@Inject @Named(\"wrappingObjectMapper\") ObjectMapper objectMapper;`\n- Add `import jakarta.inject.Named;`\n\n### 7. InfrastructureExceptionMapper.java (src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/web/mapper/InfrastructureExceptionMapper.java)\n- Change `@Inject ObjectMapper objectMapper;` to `@Inject @Named(\"wrappingObjectMapper\") ObjectMapper objectMapper;`\n- Add `import jakarta.inject.Named;`\n\n### 8. BeanValidationExceptionMapper.java (src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/web/mapper/BeanValidationExceptionMapper.java)\n- Change `@Inject ObjectMapper objectMapper;` to `@Inject @Named(\"wrappingObjectMapper\") ObjectMapper objectMapper;`\n- Add `import jakarta.inject.Named;`\n\n### 9. AuthenticationFilter.java (src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/web/security/filter/AuthenticationFilter.java)\n- Remove `@Context private ResourceInfo resourceInfo;` and change it to `@Inject ResourceInfo resourceInfo;` (Quarkus uses @Inject for ResourceInfo in filters)\n- Actually, in Quarkus REST (RESTEasy Reactive), ContainerRequestFilter works differently. The ResourceInfo can be obtained from the ContainerRequestContext. Let me think about this...\n\nActually, for Quarkus RESTEasy Reactive, the ContainerRequestFilter approach with @NameBinding works BUT @Context injection for ResourceInfo doesn't work the same way. We need to use a different approach.\n\nThe best approach for Quarkus is:\n- Keep AuthenticationFilter and AuthorizationFilter as ContainerRequestFilter implementations\n- Instead of `@Context private ResourceInfo resourceInfo;`, inject it with `@Context ResourceInfo resourceInfo;` (remove private)\n- OR better yet, use `@Inject` instead of `@Context`\n\n### 10. AuthorizationFilter.java (src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/web/security/filter/AuthorizationFilter.java)\n- Same as above: change `@Context private ResourceInfo resourceInfo;` to `@Context ResourceInfo resourceInfo;` (remove private)\n\n### 11. ALL DAO classes - Remove `private` from @Inject fields:\n- ArticleDAO.java: `@Inject private EntityUtils entityUtils;` -> `@Inject EntityUtils entityUtils;`\n- UserDAO.java: `@Inject private EntityUtils entityUtils;` -> `@Inject EntityUtils entityUtils;`\n- CommentDAO.java: `@Inject private EntityUtils entityUtils;` -> `@Inject EntityUtils entityUtils;`\n- FavoriteRelationshipDAO.java: `@Inject private EntityUtils entityUtils;` -> `@Inject EntityUtils entityUtils;`\n- FollowRelationshipDAO.java: `@Inject private EntityUtils entityUtils;` -> `@Inject EntityUtils entityUtils;`\n- TagDAO.java: `@Inject private EntityUtils entityUtils;` -> `@Inject EntityUtils entityUtils;`\n- TagRelationshipDAO.java: `@Inject private EntityUtils entityUtils;` -> `@Inject EntityUtils entityUtils;`\n\n### 12. EntityUtils.java (src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/entity/EntityUtils.java)\n- Remove `private` from all `@Inject` fields\n\n### 13. ModelValidator.java (src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/domain/validator/ModelValidator.java)\n- Remove `private` from `@Inject private Validator validator;`\n\n### 14. ALL Feature Implementation classes in domain/feature/impl/:\n- Remove `private` from all `@Inject` fields in ALL implementation files\n\n### 15. JwtTokenProvider.java - Leave as is (uses constructor injection which works fine in Quarkus with @ConfigProperty from MicroProfile Config, which Quarkus supports)\n\n### 16. SlugifySlugProvider.java - Leave as is (constructor injection)\n\n### 17. ALL builder classes:\n- ArticleModelBuilder.java: Remove `private` from `@Inject private ModelValidator modelValidator;`\n- UserModelBuilder.java: Remove `private` from `@Inject private ModelValidator modelValidator;`\n- CommentBuilder.java: Remove `private` from `@Inject private ModelValidator modelValidator;`\n- TagBuilder.java: Remove `private` from `@Inject private ModelValidator modelValidator;`\n\n## IMPORTANT RULES:\n- Read each file first before editing\n- Use Edit tool to make changes\n- For \"remove private\", change `@Inject\\n    private` pattern to `@Inject\\n    ` pattern (just remove the word \"private \")\n- For adding @Named, add it on the same line as @Inject or as a separate annotation\n\nMake ALL these changes. Start with the resource files, then the mapper files, then the filter files, then the DAO files, then the domain files."}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1441,"cache_read_input_tokens":109751,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1441,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":1983},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e4f0ba96-c3d7-44ae-b77e-aba0b53da63a","uuid":"0e97dcfd-f16f-42e3-bbdc-25141dcc37aa"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I'm migrating a Jakarta EE / Open Liberty application to Quarkus. The project root is: /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output\n\nI need you to make the following changes to multiple files. Read each file first, then edit it.\n\n## KEY CHANGES NEEDED:\n\n### 1. ArticlesResource.java (src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/ArticlesResource.java)\n- Change `@Inject ObjectMapper objectMapper;` to `@Inject @Named(\"wrappingObjectMapper\") ObjectMapper objectMapper;`\n- Add `import jakarta.inject.Named;`\n- Remove `private` from all `@Inject` fields (Quarkus CDI requires package-private or public for injection)\n\n### 2. UsersResource.java (src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/UsersResource.java)\n- Change `@Inject private ObjectMapper objectMapper;` to `@Inject @Named(\"wrappingObjectMapper\") ObjectMapper objectMapper;`\n- Add `import jakarta.inject.Named;`\n- Remove `private` from all `@Inject` fields\n- FIX BUG: The `create` method parameter has `@Context SecurityException context` - this should be `@Context SecurityContext securityContext` (but it's unused, so just keep it or remove it)\n\n### 3. UserResource.java (src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/UserResource.java)\n- Change `@Inject private ObjectMapper objectMapper;` to `@Inject @Named(\"wrappingObjectMapper\") ObjectMapper objectMapper;`\n- Add `import jakarta.inject.Named;`\n- Remove `private` from all `@Inject` fields\n\n### 4. ProfilesResource.java (src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/ProfilesResource.java)\n- Change `@Inject private ObjectMapper objectMapper;` to `@Inject @Named(\"wrappingObjectMapper\") ObjectMapper objectMapper;`\n- Add `import jakarta.inject.Named;`\n- Remove `private` from all `@Inject` fields\n\n### 5. ResourceUtils.java (src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/utils/ResourceUtils.java)\n- Remove `private` from all `@Inject` fields\n\n### 6. BusinessExceptionMapper.java (src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/web/mapper/BusinessExceptionMapper.java)\n- Change `@Inject ObjectMapper objectMapper;` to `@Inject @Named(\"wrappingObjectMapper\") ObjectMapper objectMapper;`\n- Add `import jakarta.inject.Named;`\n\n### 7. InfrastructureExceptionMapper.java (src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/web/mapper/InfrastructureExceptionMapper.java)\n- Change `@Inject ObjectMapper objectMapper;` to `@Inject @Named(\"wrappingObjectMapper\") ObjectMapper objectMapper;`\n- Add `import jakarta.inject.Named;`\n\n### 8. BeanValidationExceptionMapper.java (src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/web/mapper/BeanValidationExceptionMapper.java)\n- Change `@Inject ObjectMapper objectMapper;` to `@Inject @Named(\"wrappingObjectMapper\") ObjectMapper objectMapper;`\n- Add `import jakarta.inject.Named;`\n\n### 9. AuthenticationFilter.java (src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/web/security/filter/AuthenticationFilter.java)\n- Remove `@Context private ResourceInfo resourceInfo;` and change it to `@Inject ResourceInfo resourceInfo;` (Quarkus uses @Inject for ResourceInfo in filters)\n- Actually, in Quarkus REST (RESTEasy Reactive), ContainerRequestFilter works differently. The ResourceInfo can be obtained from the ContainerRequestContext. Let me think about this...\n\nActually, for Quarkus RESTEasy Reactive, the ContainerRequestFilter approach with @NameBinding works BUT @Context injection for ResourceInfo doesn't work the same way. We need to use a different approach.\n\nThe best approach for Quarkus is:\n- Keep AuthenticationFilter and AuthorizationFilter as ContainerRequestFilter implementations\n- Instead of `@Context private ResourceInfo resourceInfo;`, inject it with `@Context ResourceInfo resourceInfo;` (remove private)\n- OR better yet, use `@Inject` instead of `@Context`\n\n### 10. AuthorizationFilter.java (src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/web/security/filter/AuthorizationFilter.java)\n- Same as above: change `@Context private ResourceInfo resourceInfo;` to `@Context ResourceInfo resourceInfo;` (remove private)\n\n### 11. ALL DAO classes - Remove `private` from @Inject fields:\n- ArticleDAO.java: `@Inject private EntityUtils entityUtils;` -> `@Inject EntityUtils entityUtils;`\n- UserDAO.java: `@Inject private EntityUtils entityUtils;` -> `@Inject EntityUtils entityUtils;`\n- CommentDAO.java: `@Inject private EntityUtils entityUtils;` -> `@Inject EntityUtils entityUtils;`\n- FavoriteRelationshipDAO.java: `@Inject private EntityUtils entityUtils;` -> `@Inject EntityUtils entityUtils;`\n- FollowRelationshipDAO.java: `@Inject private EntityUtils entityUtils;` -> `@Inject EntityUtils entityUtils;`\n- TagDAO.java: `@Inject private EntityUtils entityUtils;` -> `@Inject EntityUtils entityUtils;`\n- TagRelationshipDAO.java: `@Inject private EntityUtils entityUtils;` -> `@Inject EntityUtils entityUtils;`\n\n### 12. EntityUtils.java (src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/entity/EntityUtils.java)\n- Remove `private` from all `@Inject` fields\n\n### 13. ModelValidator.java (src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/domain/validator/ModelValidator.java)\n- Remove `private` from `@Inject private Validator validator;`\n\n### 14. ALL Feature Implementation classes in domain/feature/impl/:\n- Remove `private` from all `@Inject` fields in ALL implementation files\n\n### 15. JwtTokenProvider.java - Leave as is (uses constructor injection which works fine in Quarkus with @ConfigProperty from MicroProfile Config, which Quarkus supports)\n\n### 16. SlugifySlugProvider.java - Leave as is (constructor injection)\n\n### 17. ALL builder classes:\n- ArticleModelBuilder.java: Remove `private` from `@Inject private ModelValidator modelValidator;`\n- UserModelBuilder.java: Remove `private` from `@Inject private ModelValidator modelValidator;`\n- CommentBuilder.java: Remove `private` from `@Inject private ModelValidator modelValidator;`\n- TagBuilder.java: Remove `private` from `@Inject private ModelValidator modelValidator;`\n\n## IMPORTANT RULES:\n- Read each file first before editing\n- Use Edit tool to make changes\n- For \"remove private\", change `@Inject\\n    private` pattern to `@Inject\\n    ` pattern (just remove the word \"private \")\n- For adding @Named, add it on the same line as @Inject or as a separate annotation\n\nMake ALL these changes. Start with the resource files, then the mapper files, then the filter files, then the DAO files, then the domain files."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_012AGQbfMpSF8tyKV9Zw5HuZ","session_id":"e4f0ba96-c3d7-44ae-b77e-aba0b53da63a","uuid":"ea664815-287d-44e9-b7bc-dd84bf3d40d3"}
