{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_012AGQbfMpSF8tyKV9Zw5HuZ","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! All the necessary changes have been made. Let me create a summary of all the changes:\n\n## Summary\n\nI have successfully completed all the requested changes to migrate this Jakarta EE / Open Liberty application to Quarkus. Here's what was modified:\n\n### 1. Resource Files (Added `@Named(\"wrappingObjectMapper\")` and removed `private` from `@Inject` fields)\n- **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/ArticlesResource.java**\n  - Added `import jakarta.inject.Named;`\n  - Changed `@Inject ObjectMapper objectMapper;` to `@Inject @Named(\"wrappingObjectMapper\") ObjectMapper objectMapper;`\n  - Removed `private` from all `@Inject` fields\n\n- **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/UsersResource.java**\n  - Added `import jakarta.inject.Named;`\n  - Changed `@Inject private ObjectMapper objectMapper;` to `@Inject @Named(\"wrappingObjectMapper\") ObjectMapper objectMapper;`\n  - Removed `private` from all `@Inject` fields\n  - Fixed bug: Changed `@Context SecurityException context` to `@Context SecurityContext securityContext`\n\n- **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/UserResource.java**\n  - Added `import jakarta.inject.Named;`\n  - Changed `@Inject private ObjectMapper objectMapper;` to `@Inject @Named(\"wrappingObjectMapper\") ObjectMapper objectMapper;`\n  - Removed `private` from all `@Inject` fields\n\n- **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/sca