{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01WnSrFm2RrgSshRRbeJ4wBe","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A 400 with empty body. The issue is that the deserialization is failing. In Quarkus RESTEasy Reactive with Jackson, when the request body can't be deserialized, it returns a 400. The problem might be that the Quarkus Jackson ObjectMapper is configured differently.\n\nActually, I think I know the problem. The resource method was using the `wrappingObjectMapper` for serializing responses, which has `UNWRAP_ROOT_VALUE` enabled. But Quarkus REST uses its own ObjectMapper for request deserialization - the default one. The `NewUserRequestWrapper` expects `{\"user\": {...}}` which should work fine with the default ObjectMapper (the field is called `user`).\n\nWait - I bet the issue is that the Quarkus default ObjectMapper might be interfering with our custom producer. In Quarkus, when you produce custom `ObjectMapper` beans, they can conflict with Quarkus's built-in one. Let me create a `ObjectMapperCustomizer` instead, which is the Quarkus way:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":495,"cache_read_input_tokens":152327,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":495,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":522},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e4f0ba96-c3d7-44ae-b77e-aba0b53da63a","uuid":"912ba88c-cc1a-4cf6-9389-52b5f6975370"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01WnSrFm2RrgSshRRbeJ4wBe","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_013ApsEvNCWYVntKpL64L6y5","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/config/ObjectMapperConfig.java","content":"package org.example.realworldapi.infrastructure.config;\n\nimport com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.ObjectMapper;\nimport com.fasterxml.jackson.datatype.jsr310.JavaTimeModule;\nimport io.quarkus.jackson.ObjectMapperCustomizer;\nimport jakarta.inject.Singleton;\n\n@Singleton\npublic class ObjectMapperConfig implements ObjectMapperCustomizer {\n\n    @Override\n    public void customize(ObjectMapper objectMapper) {\n        // Register JavaTimeModule for LocalDateTime serialization\n        objectMapper.registerModule(new JavaTimeModule());\n    }\n}\n"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":495,"cache_read_input_tokens":152327,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":495,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":522},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e4f0ba96-c3d7-44ae-b77e-aba0b53da63a","uuid":"e1d3550d-ef31-4f4f-867a-4f8ac6556064"}
