{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01Fu3yrSyEk2ZJqM58wFtNE9","type":"tool_result","content":"/var/run/postgresql:5432 - accepting connections\nPostgreSQL is ready\n=== Setting up database ===\nCREATE ROLE\nCREATE DATABASE\nGRANT\n=== Starting Quarkus Application ===\n=== Waiting for application ===\n__  ____  __  _____   ___  __ ____  ______ \n --/ __ \\/ / / / _ | / _ \\/ //_/ / / / __/ \n -/ /_/ / /_/ / __ |/ , _/ ,< / /_/ /\\ \\   \n--\\___\\_\\____/_/ |_/_/|_/_/|_|\\____/___/   \n2026-03-14 07:50:26,634 INFO  [io.quarkus] (main) realworld-quarkus 1.0.0 on JVM (powered by Quarkus 3.17.8) started in 3.093s. Listening on: http://0.0.0.0:8080\n2026-03-14 07:50:26,635 INFO  [io.quarkus] (main) Profile prod activated. \n2026-03-14 07:50:26,635 INFO  [io.quarkus] (main) Installed features: [agroal, cdi, hibernate-orm, hibernate-validator, jdbc-postgresql, narayana-jta, resteasy, resteasy-jackson, smallrye-context-propagation, smallrye-health, vertx]\nApplication is ready!\n=== Running Smoke Tests ===\n2026-03-14 07:50:28,085 ERROR [org.jbo.res.plu.pro.jackson] (executor-thread-1) RESTEASY-JACKSON000100: Not able to deserialize data provided: com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.exc.MismatchedInputException: Root name ('user') does not match expected ('NewUserRequestWrapper') for type `org.example.realworldapi.application.web.model.request.NewUserRequestWrapper`\n at [Source: REDACTED (`StreamReadFeature.INCLUDE_SOURCE_IN_LOCATION` disabled); line: 1, column: 2] (through reference chain: org.example.realworldapi.application.web.model.request.NewUserRequestWrapper[\"user\"])\n\tat com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.exc.MismatchedInputException.from(MismatchedInputException.java:63)\n\tat com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.DeserializationContext.reportPropertyInputMismatch(DeserializationContext.java:1802)\n\tat com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.DeserializationContext.reportPropertyInputMismatch(DeserializationContext.java:1818)\n\tat com.fasterx