{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01Bbk6sxd2m1mGsiQsKmP4Eu","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I can see the exact error. The root cause is clear:\n\n```\nRoot name ('user') does not match expected ('NewUserRequestWrapper') for type `org.example.realworldapi.application.web.model.request.NewUserRequestWrapper`\n```\n\nThe problem is that the Quarkus/RESTEasy Jackson provider is using the **wrapping ObjectMapper** (with `UNWRAP_ROOT_VALUE` enabled) for request deserialization! The `UNWRAP_ROOT_VALUE` feature tries to unwrap the root element from JSON, and it expects the root name to match the class name (`NewUserRequestWrapper`), but the JSON has `\"user\"` as the root key.\n\nThis confirms that the CDI-produced `@Named(\"wrappingObjectMapper\")` bean is being picked up by RESTEasy's Jackson provider as the ObjectMapper for deserialization. The `@Named` qualifier is not sufficient - RESTEasy Classic looks for any `ObjectMapper` bean in CDI.\n\nThe fix is clear: I need to prevent the wrapping ObjectMapper from being picked up by RESTEasy's Jackson provider. The cleanest approach is to:\n\n1. **Not produce ObjectMapper as a CDI bean** - instead, create it manually in a helper class\n2. OR use the `ObjectMapperCustomizer` approach for the default ObjectMapper and handle wrapping separately\n\nLet me take approach 1 - change `SerializerConfig` to not use `@Produces` for the wrapping ObjectMapper, and instead make it a direct singleton that resources can use via injection of the config class itself:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2320,"cache_read_input_tokens":88012,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":2320,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":484},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e4f0ba96-c3d7-44ae-b77e-aba0b53da63a","uuid":"fefbe923-4582-4cbf-8eb3-53e1f96ae6c4"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01Bbk6sxd2m1mGsiQsKmP4Eu","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01McxYYniNbA2GNfkoPSibrL","name":"Read","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/config/SerializerConfig.java"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2320,"cache_read_input_tokens":88012,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":2320,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":484},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e4f0ba96-c3d7-44ae-b77e-aba0b53da63a","uuid":"53e3d540-cc47-42ea-9d39-aa60a996921d"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01McxYYniNbA2GNfkoPSibrL","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→package org.example.realworldapi.infrastructure.config;\n     2→\n     3→import com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.DeserializationFeature;\n     4→import com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.ObjectMapper;\n     5→import com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.SerializationFeature;\n     6→import com.fasterxml.jackson.datatype.jsr310.JavaTimeModule;\n     7→import io.quarkus.arc.Unremovable;\n     8→import jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped;\n     9→import jakarta.enterprise.inject.Produces;\n    10→import jakarta.inject.Named;\n    11→import jakarta.inject.Singleton;\n    12→import org.example.realworldapi.infrastructure.web.qualifiers.NoWrapRootValueObjectMapper;\n    13→\n    14→@ApplicationScoped\n    15→public class SerializerConfig {\n    16→\n    17→    @Singleton\n    18→    @Produces\n    19→    @Unremovable\n    20→    @Named(\"wrappingObjectMapper\")\n    21→    public ObjectMapper objectMapper() {\n    22→        ObjectMapper objectMapper = new ObjectMapper();\n    23→        objectMapper.enable(SerializationFeature.WRAP_ROOT_VALUE);\n    24→        objectMapper.enable(DeserializationFeature.UNWRAP_ROOT_VALUE);\n    25→        objectMapper.registerModule(new JavaTimeModule());\n    26→        return objectMapper;\n    27→    }\n    28→\n    29→    @Singleton\n    30→    @Produces\n    31→    @Unremovable\n    32→    @NoWrapRootValueObjectMapper\n    33→    public ObjectMapper noWrapRootValueObjectMapper() {\n    34→        return new ObjectMapper().registerModule(new JavaTimeModule());\n    35→    }\n    36→\n    37→}\n    38→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e4f0ba96-c3d7-44ae-b77e-aba0b53da63a","uuid":"82920e2f-71d6-4634-9576-3598c6a5cf90"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01YCKb6Zc28beo98ytRaxNhW","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The issue is clear now. The `@Named(\"wrappingObjectMapper\")` ObjectMapper is still picked up by RESTEasy because `@Named` doesn't prevent it from being considered as an ObjectMapper bean. RESTEasy's `ResteasyJackson2Provider` uses CDI to look up ObjectMapper and it finds this one.\n\nI need to completely remove the `@Produces` ObjectMapper beans and instead manage the ObjectMapper instances manually. The resources that need them will get them through the `SerializerConfig` instance directly.\n\nLet me rewrite `SerializerConfig` to provide the ObjectMapper instances as regular methods (not CDI producers), and update all injection sites:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1059,"cache_read_input_tokens":90332,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1059,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":623},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e4f0ba96-c3d7-44ae-b77e-aba0b53da63a","uuid":"063ebafb-d37d-44b0-8169-518a8e4c8151"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01YCKb6Zc28beo98ytRaxNhW","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01LzdYqkGh1rkGDyDDPawvjr","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__quarkus/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/config/SerializerConfig.java","content":"package org.example.realworldapi.infrastructure.config;\n\nimport com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.DeserializationFeature;\nimport com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.ObjectMapper;\nimport com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.SerializationFeature;\nimport com.fasterxml.jackson.datatype.jsr310.JavaTimeModule;\nimport jakarta.inject.Singleton;\n\n@Singleton\npublic class SerializerConfig {\n\n    private final ObjectMapper wrappingObjectMapper;\n    private final ObjectMapper noWrapRootValueObjectMapper;\n\n    public SerializerConfig() {\n        this.wrappingObjectMapper = new ObjectMapper();\n        this.wrappingObjectMapper.enable(SerializationFeature.WRAP_ROOT_VALUE);\n        this.wrappingObjectMapper.enable(DeserializationFeature.UNWRAP_ROOT_VALUE);\n        this.wrappingObjectMapper.registerModule(new JavaTimeModule());\n\n        this.noWrapRootValueObjectMapper = new ObjectMapper();\n        this.noWrapRootValueObjectMapper.registerModule(new JavaTimeModule());\n    }\n\n    public ObjectMapper getWrappingObjectMapper() {\n        return wrappingObjectMapper;\n    }\n\n    public ObjectMapper getNoWrapRootValueObjectMapper() {\n        return noWrapRootValueObjectMapper;\n    }\n}\n"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1059,"cache_read_input_tokens":90332,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1059,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":623},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e4f0ba96-c3d7-44ae-b77e-aba0b53da63a","uuid":"c2550782-4933-47b0-a9d8-01a3b913cc6d"}
