{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01HkFZ5vnsVuiYUHSWvoHmyP","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The migration is complete. Here's the summary:\n\n## Migration Complete: Jakarta EE (Open Liberty) to Quarkus\n\n### Results\n- **Build**: SUCCESS (Quarkus 3.17.8 with `quarkus-resteasy-jackson`)\n- **Docker**: Image built and container running\n- **Tests**: **58/58 passed, 0 failed**\n\n### Key Changes Made\n1. **pom.xml**: Replaced all Jakarta EE/Liberty dependencies with Quarkus extensions; changed packaging from WAR to JAR\n2. **application.properties**: Created Quarkus config (datasource, Hibernate ORM, JWT, CORS)\n3. **CDI**: Removed `private` from all `@Inject` fields (Quarkus Arc requirement); changed `@PersistenceContext` to `@Inject`\n4. **ObjectMapper conflict fix**: Removed CDI `@Produces` ObjectMapper beans that interfered with RESTEasy's built-in Jackson provider; wrapped them in `SerializerConfig` as plain getters\n5. **RESTEasy Classic**: Used `quarkus-resteasy-jackson` (Classic) instead of `quarkus-rest-jackson` (Reactive) for full compatibility with `@NameBinding`, `@Context ResourceInfo`, and `ContainerRequestFilter`\n6. **Dockerfile/start.sh**: Updated for Quarkus runtime (Temurin JDK, `java -jar` instead of Liberty)\n7. **Removed**: Liberty config files (`server.xml`, `persistence.xml`, `beans.xml`, `microprofile-config.properties`), Liberty-specific tests\n\n### Critical Bug Fixed\nThe main challenge was a CDI ObjectMapper bean conflict where RESTEasy picked up the wrapping ObjectMapper (with `UNWRAP_ROOT_VALUE`) for request deserialization, causing HTTP 400 on all POST endpoints. Fixed by removing `@Produces` from the ObjectMapper beans and using a service class pattern instead."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":434,"cache_read_input_tokens":131021,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":434,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":463},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e4f0ba96-c3d7-44ae-b77e-aba0b53da63a","uuid":"f08aad1f-7518-42ff-9948-f3cf80e1d3b8"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":3652515,"duration_api_ms":3425649,"num_turns":177,"result":"The migration is complete. Here's the summary:\n\n## Migration Complete: Jakarta EE (Open Liberty) to Quarkus\n\n### Results\n- **Build**: SUCCESS (Quarkus 3.17.8 with `quarkus-resteasy-jackson`)\n- **Docker**: Image built and container running\n- **Tests**: **58/58 passed, 0 failed**\n\n### Key Changes Made\n1. **pom.xml**: Replaced all Jakarta EE/Liberty dependencies with Quarkus extensions; changed packaging from WAR to JAR\n2. **application.properties**: Created Quarkus config (datasource, Hibernate ORM, JWT, CORS)\n3. **CDI**: Removed `private` from all `@Inject` fields (Quarkus Arc requirement); changed `@PersistenceContext` to `@Inject`\n4. **ObjectMapper conflict fix**: Removed CDI `@Produces` ObjectMapper beans that interfered with RESTEasy's built-in Jackson provider; wrapped them in `SerializerConfig` as plain getters\n5. **RESTEasy Classic**: Used `quarkus-resteasy-jackson` (Classic) instead of `quarkus-rest-jackson` (Reactive) for full compatibility with `@NameBinding`, `@Context ResourceInfo`, and `ContainerRequestFilter`\n6. **Dockerfile/start.sh**: Updated for Quarkus runtime (Temurin JDK, `java -jar` instead of Liberty)\n7. **Removed**: Liberty config files (`server.xml`, `persistence.xml`, `beans.xml`, `microprofile-config.properties`), Liberty-specific tests\n\n### Critical Bug Fixed\nThe main challenge was a CDI ObjectMapper bean conflict where RESTEasy picked up the wrapping ObjectMapper (with `UNWRAP_ROOT_VALUE`) for request deserialization, causing HTTP 400 on all POST endpoints. Fixed by removing `@Produces` from the ObjectMapper beans and using a service class pattern instead.","session_id":"e4f0ba96-c3d7-44ae-b77e-aba0b53da63a","total_cost_usd":37.42616160999998,"usage":{"input_tokens":421,"cache_creation_input_tokens":357573,"cache_read_input_tokens":11539659,"output_tokens":60906,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_re